extends ./layout
block title
  title px-mobile | Getting Started
block content 
  .hero.container.full-width
    .col-12.text-center
      h1 Getting Started
      p Once you download px-mobile, here's what you need to do next.
  .container.full-width.gutters
    .col-12
      h2 Quick Start
      p Here are is a few easy ways to quickly get started, each one appealing to a different skill level and use case. Read through to see what suits your particular needs.
      
      h3 Install with Bower
      p Use bower to simplify the installation process, open the terminal and execute the following:

      pre
        $ bower install https://github.build.ge.com/PredixComponents/px-mobile.git --save
        
    
//
